    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-11-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-11-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="78"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d78">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Thompson</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-11-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 17, 1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Gresham instructs Mr. Thompson to join in the request, which should be made
                    to both parties, if the floating torpedoes are proving a damage to neutral
                    vessels, that they permit the removal of those torpedoes.</p>
            </div>
